          "reviewBody": "The School has good infrastructure and spatious classrooms with various activities conducted for all occasions like Diwali,Pongal. About the studies, the portions are much advanced and teachers train the students in unique way and make them understand with the practical methods. In my experience, I would say this is one of the best school.",
